r"""
The set $\PP^1(\Q)$ of cusps

EXAMPLES:
    sage: Cusps()
    The set P^1(Q) of cusps.

    sage: Cusp(oo)
    Infinity
"""

#*****************************************************************************
#       Copyright (C) 2005 William Stein <wstein@ucsd.edu>
